cial complaint\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"the Attorney General\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the participation\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"ineligible athletes\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic boxing tournament\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA statement continued: \\\"According to the Swiss law, any action or inaction that poses a safety risk to competition participants warrants investigation and may serve as grounds for criminal prosecution.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9537303509242088, \"rank\": 0.04851439224264748, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999986685874996, \"rank\": 1.3314142623501426e-06, \"text\": \"Swiss law\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"inaction\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"a safety risk\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"competition participants warrants investigation\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"grounds\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"criminal prosecution\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, similar complaints are to be filed with the Attorneys General of France and the USA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7715962602065962, \"rank\": 0.283090750462208,