\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"statement\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medalist boxer\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"astatement\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"Instagramon\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"sacrifice\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have earned my place, and I will continue to stand firm in the face of any challenge.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my place\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"any challenge\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For two years, I have taken the high road while my name and image have been used, unauthorized, to further personal and political agendas through the spreading and dissemination of baseless lies and misinformation.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the high road\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"image\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"further personal and political agendas\", \"from\":